<span class="usa-tag pmc-tag-pt">letter</span> <div class="display-inline-block"><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer text-no-underline bg-transparent border-0 padding-0 text-left margin-0 text-normal text-primary" aria-controls="journal_context_menu">Br J Cancer</button></div>. 2008 Sep 16;99(8):1302–1306. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/sj.bjc.6604644" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1038/sj.bjc.6604644</a>
</div>
