<hgroup><h1>
<em>In vitro</em> phosphorylation of BRCA2 by the checkpoint kinase CHEK2</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Kim%20S%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">S Kim</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">S Kim</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Massachusetts General Hospital Cancer Center, Harvard Medical School, Massachusetts General Hospital, Charlestown, MA 02129, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Kim%20S%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link"><span class="name western">S Kim</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Mohapatra%20G%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">G Mohapatra</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">G Mohapatra</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Pathology, Harvard Medical School, Massachusetts General Hospital, Charlestown, MA 02129, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Mohapatra%20G%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link"><span class="name western">G Mohapatra</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Haber%20DA%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">D A Haber</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">D A Haber</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Massachusetts General Hospital Cancer Center, Harvard Medical School, Massachusetts General Hospital, Charlestown, MA 02129, USA</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Haber%20DA%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link"><span class="name western">D A Haber</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>*</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
